description: If there's one thing that France is known for, it's amazing food, so there's nothing more French on the streets of San Jose than this food truck!Elle's Crepes & Galettes is the perfect food truck for anyone looking for a taste of European tradition. Crepes have always been a great food for any occasion, whether it's an awesome outdoor party or just a day out on the town. If you're in the mood for something savory, then the Brie Cheese, Vegetarian, and Spicy Chorizo are sure to satisfy. For those with a bit more of a sweet tooth, the Lemon Tart, Caramel, and Banana & Nutella crepes are absolute perfection.Serving something for everyone, Elle's Crepes & Galettes will never disappoint.
name: Elle's Crepes & Galettes
